
Fetch Data Query
Query to fetch all credit cards:
query {
    allCreditCards {
        id
        cardNumber
        cardHolderName
        expirationDate
        cvv
    }
}
Query to fetch a specific credit card by ID:
query {
    getCreditCard(id: "1") {
        id
        cardNumber
        cardHolderName
        expirationDate
        cvv
    }
}
Query to fetch paginated credit cards:
query {
    paginatedCreditCards(page: 0, size: 10) {
        id
        cardNumber
        cardHolderName
        expirationDate
        cvv
    }
}
Insert Data Mutation
Mutation to insert a new credit card:
mutation {
    createCreditCard(
        cardNumber: "1234567812345678",
        cardHolderName: "John Doe",
        expirationDate: "12/25",
        cvv: "123"
    ) {
        id
        cardNumber
        cardHolderName
        expirationDate
        cvv
    }
}
